{"tid":856142,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無諗過韓潮過後啲人選擇迷支兩登都有一定責任","createTime":"2018-10-10T11:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T06:26:55.000Z","uid":92376,"like":10,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2acc7a970c44322b7e6a3533fb4aabcae7552f23","tid":856142,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T11:59:39.000Z","msg":"依家就話啲00後迷支那明星好墮落<br />\n但唔迷韓之後本來我以為會變左吹泰風<br />\n但由高到連登<br />\n一個二個見到泰妹就話人地有丁<br />\n就算有好靚既女 啲人都比你地講到唔敢鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁搞搞下迷完韓國啲人自然搵其他野黎迷，咁啱呢個趨勢就揀中左支那星，當然背後仲有好多原因影響啦，但兩登確實係有一定責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：副ig follow左唔少靚同省鏡既thaimay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7e9a068949a80da0fdabab7ec9295a911b827d","tid":856142,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:38:37.000Z","msg":"啱呀，而家好多細路抗拒韓流，成日講人造人、淫舞、洗腦歌同白面仔，但又唔係追歐美、日本、台灣，而係追支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc2b060335f736e6c457d2c66c70495e28455b6","tid":856142,"uid":52073,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"以前我係高登都係祟日既激進派 直到我遇到twice..."},{"pid":"cb148eb8820b996401e88daadaca500d62e49605","tid":856142,"uid":115441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"中國根本韓國2.0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只不過中國好多野抄韓國<br />\n尤其是d綜藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5884112123efcfa044b8e43df2f569febdcfc7a7","tid":856142,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"而家中國已經好過以前好多 唔好咁井底之蛙"},{"pid":"ac8549c89428934db9e92b766a524f37ae089458","tid":856142,"uid":213300,"like":6,"dislike":12,